instructions: Go to Settings , then do one of the following: iPhone X and later: Tap Face ID & Passcode. Other models: Tap Touch ID & Passcode. Tap Turn Passcode On or Change Passcode.
Go to Settings , then do one of the following: iPhone X and later: Tap Face ID & Passcode. Other models: Tap Touch ID & Passcode. Turn on Erase Data.
Go to Settings , then do one of the following: iPhone X and later: Tap Face ID & Passcode. Other models: Tap Touch ID & Passcode. Tap Turn Passcode Off.
